item.title: Project1
item.description: Since quarantine started, I have been bouncing between new and old hobbies and getting invested in them more than normally. Most reently, this passion has been towards soccer. Growing up, it was the main sport I played all the way up until part way through highschool when I stopped having the time to keep up all of my hobbies. Therefore, I decided to look for some datasets in relation to this for inspiration.
